  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "QA Engineer (IPQC / FA)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Manage IPQC Lab and FA/CoC team</p></li><li><p>Work with internal team to Identify root cause of issues and develop CAPA.</p></li><li><p>Verify CAPA implementation / effectiveness.</p></li><li><p>Review Customer specifications, Drawing and translate onto checklist.</p></li><li><p>Review quality documentation ( WI, Control Plan, Customer Specific Requirements)</p></li><li><p>Track quality assurance goals (LAT Yield (x-section).</p></li><li><p>Lead a group of IPQC Inspectors & FA Technician to carry out in-process inspection as per requirements.</p></li><li><p>Participate in Quality Improvement Program</p></li><li><p>Conduct training to fellow colleagues, peers and /or subordinates.</p></li><li><p>Any other tasks assigned by department lead.<br /></p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum Degree or Diploma in Computer Science or Engineering.</p></li><li><p>Minimum 2-years experience in manufacturing</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of tools, concepts and methodologies of QA (ISO 9001, 7 QC tools and etc)</p></li><li><p>Team player and good communication skill</p></li></ul>",
